Legendary director Martin Scorsese’s Fox Nation series, ‘The Saints,’ returns for Season 2 this November, featuring new episodes on iconic saints from Peter to the newly-minted Saint Carlo Acutis.
Actor Desmond Eastwood joins 'Fox & Friends' to preview season two of FOX Nation's 'The Saints.'
Actor Desmond Eastwood brings St. Patrick's incredible journey to life in Fox Nation's "The Saints." Discover the true story behind Ireland's patron saint.
From acclaimed director Martin Scorsese, the Season 2 premiere of ‘The Saints’ explores St. Patrick’s transformation from slave to bishop — and his lasting impact on Ireland and Christianity.
Alexa Anderson stepped off the podium to protest a trans athlete at Oregon's state championship and filed a lawsuit against OSAA over alleged medal withholding.
Oregon high school track and field medalist Alexa Anderson reveals how long her medal was kept from her after protesting trans athlete, and the death threats she received in the aftermath.
Fox Nation uncovers St. Patrick's legacy as Ireland's influential bishop in the first episode of the second season of "The Saints," helmed by film icon Martin Scorsese.
Actor Desmond Eastwood discusses his experience working on Fox Nation's 'The Saints' on 'America Reports.'
Country star Kix Brooks and head winemaker of Lazarre Wines, Adam Lazarre, join 'Fox & Friends' to promote 'Wine Nation,' a three-part series hosted by Abby Hornacek on Fox Nation.
The 'Outnumbered' panel reacts to the season two trailer of Martin Scorsese's 'The Saints,' and delves into the history behind it. 'The Saints' season two premieres Sunday 11/16 on Fox Nation.
Francesca Scorsese is following in her legendary father’s footsteps, making her Fox Nation directorial debut with an episode of “Martin Scorsese Presents: The Saints."
Join the exclusive streaming service brought to you by Fox News, with entertaining and informative shows that highlight the unique stories, history, and people of America.
